### Welcome to Open Source at Wesleyan University!
This page aggregates all the open source projects developed by the bright minds of the greater [Wesleyan](http://www.wesleyan.edu) community.

### Projects
+ [cmdr](http://wesleyan.github.io/cmdr): An A/V control system built in Ruby with an HTML5 frontend
+ [spec](http://wesleyan.github.io/spec): Describe spec here!
+ [pulleffect](http://wesleyan.github.io/pulleffect): Describe pulleffect here!

### Current Contributors
+ Robert Christensen (@rchristensen)
+ Brent Morgan (@brentmorgan)
+ Brian Gapinski '14 (@bgapinski)

+ Sam Giagtzoglou '16 (@samgiagtzoglou)

+ Erik Islo '15 (@jacthinman)
